---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="WorshipMetrics Privacy Policy."
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10">Last updated: January 1, 2025</p>
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-10">
          This Privacy Policy describes how WorshipMetrics collects, uses, and protects your
          information when you use our services.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-10">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We collect information you provide directly (name, email, church details),
              information generated by your use of our services (attendance records, member data
              you enter), and technical information (device type, browser, usage patterns) to
              provide and improve our services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We use your information to provide the WorshipMetrics service, send transactional
              emails, improve the platform, and communicate with you about your account. We do not
              sell your data to third parties.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">3. Data Retention</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Free Forever plan data is retained for 90 days of inactivity. Paid plan data is retained for
              the duration of your subscription plus 30 days after cancellation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">4. Security</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We use industry-standard encryption and security practices. Your church and member
              data is stored securely and access is controlled through role-based permissions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">5. Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Questions about this policy? Email{" "}
              <a href="mailto:paul@worshipmetrics.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 underline">
                paul@worshipmetrics.com
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
